# Font Size Demo
# Shows different font size options

Output examples/dvds/font-sizes.svg

Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set FontSize 20
Set Title "Large Font Demo"

Type "# This uses a 20px font"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "echo 'Great for presentations and readability!'"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
